    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cordelia is a princess with a heart too big to fit inside her body. She must follow her heart to defeat the <strong>Ice Queen</strong> and her cold creature creations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the ever changing lands and go on an platforming adventure with many different obstacles to overcome and secrets to find.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain mysterious items to aid you in your quest to find if true love really exist in a cold world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every game played is a new adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handcrafted levels gets scrambled with a new level layout to make each run unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerful items and loot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world filled with loot and powerful items and you never know what you get.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Retro fantasy adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Inspired by old-school graphics, aesthetics and gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mysterious lands</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse strange lands that are vastly different from each other. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385680/extras/fe1e1bc2de872dbfd0de2829c1e977ec.webp?t=1745835410\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p>",
